SUMMARY:Performing Arts School Honors Recital
DESCRIPTION:Performing Arts School Honors Recital\nMay 3\, 2026 at 3:00 p.m.\nSaint John’s Lutheran Church\, Summit\nFREE Event \nJoin us for an afternoon of performances by distinguished young musicians from the Wharton Performing Arts School. \nThis arts program is made possible in part by a 2025 HEART (History\, Education\, Arts Reaching Thousands) Grant from the Union County Board of County Commissioners.
URL:https://whartonarts.org/calendar/performing-arts-school-honors-recital/
LOCATION:St. John’s Lutheran Church\, 587 Springfield Avenue\, Summit\, 07901\, United States
CATEGORIES:PAS,Wharton
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://whartonarts.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/PAS-Honors-Recital-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
