SUMMARY:NJYC: Voices Rising: Women's Choral Invitational
DESCRIPTION:NJYC: Voices Rising: Women’s Choral Invitational\nMay 2\, 2026\nFREE Event \nNJYC’s Coriste welcomes local high school women’s ensembles for an exclusive invitational workshop with composer and conductor\, Dr. Andrea Ramsey. Singers will explore innovative repertoire\, deepen their artistry\, and refine their vocal and musical skills. The day concludes with a shared performance open to the public.
URL:https://whartonarts.org/calendar/voices-rising-womens-choral-invitational/
CATEGORIES:NJYC,Wharton
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://whartonarts.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Voices-Rising-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
