DESCRIPTION:PMP: Day of Jazz\nApril 25\, 2026 at 4:00 p.m.\nJohn F. Kennedy High School\, Paterson\nFREE Event\nSuggested donation of canned or dry food. \nThe Third Annual Day of Jazz will feature all PMP jazz and contemporary ensembles along with guest bands from other Paterson Public Schools.
