DESCRIPTION:PAS: Café Choir Concert\nApril 29\, 2026 at 12:30 p.m.\nWharton Black Box Theater\, Berkeley Heights\nFREE Event \nOur Creative Aging For Everyone Choir presents a program of old hits\, classic choral works\, and showtunes. Come be inspired by this fun and lively program. \nSusan Kirkland\, Director\nPeter Hill\, Piano
