SUMMARY:NJYC Performs at Citi Field!
DESCRIPTION:Take Me Out To The Ballgame!\nJune 12\, 2026 at 7:00 p.m.\nCiti Field\, Flushing \nJoin us at Citi Field as the New Jersey Youth Chorus performs the National Anthem for the Mets’ matchup against the Atlanta Braves. Experience the thrill of live baseball as NJYC brings energy\, pride\, and musical excellence to America’s favorite pastime. Tickets at NJYC.org.
URL:https://whartonarts.org/calendar/njyc-performs-at-citi-field/
LOCATION:Citi Field\, 41 Seaver Way\, Queens\, 11368\, United States
CATEGORIES:NJYC,Wharton
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://whartonarts.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/NJYC_MetsGame.jpg
END:VEVENT
